name: blocks
description: another digital sigil. traditionally, ‘blocking’ is a technique used by past civilizations to transmit energy from one location to another. practitioners would come together and combine intentions through these self-transforming block shapes, which proved to be a more efficient form of energy work than trying to instigate change remotely. collect to attract foundational stability and general harmony. inscribed by tenorless circa 2019 // genesis collection // mp4 // 1080p x 1080p // 60fps
